snippet.title: Resident Evil 7 biohazard - Not a Hero: “Lucas" | PS4
snippet.description:
Chris Redfield comes up against new and terrifying enemies in his pursuit of a fleeing suspect in Resident Evil 7's free 'Not a Hero' DLC, coming 12/12/17.

http://residentevil7.com/us/GE/ 

Rated Mature: Strong Language, Blood and Gore, Intense Violence
